ding workplace culture, safety concerns, and legal challenges. These controversies have included allegations of worker rights violations and issues related to the deployment of its self-driving technology.\n\nIf you have any questions or need further information, feel free to reach out.\n\nBest regards,  \n[Your Name]  \n[Your Position]  \n[Your Contact Information]",
